data.description: Discover this energy-efficient 2-story gem in the esteemed Palm Valley III! Offering a large front yard, a 2-car garage, & a delightful front porch perfect for your morning coffee. Be greeted by an inviting living/dining room, tall ceilings, Saltillo tile floors, ceiling fans, & so much natural light. The open layout has a media niche & back patio access. The kitchen includes built-in appliances, recessed lighting, wood cabinetry, stylish tile backsplash, a breakfast nook, & an island w/a breakfast bar. Upstairs, the sizable loft is perfect for a hobby space. You'll love to relax in the spacious primary retreat, showcasing plush carpeting, a full bathroom w/dual sinks & a mirrored-door closet. The generous backyard has a covered patio, a desert landscape, & storage shed. Visit now!
